During her 911 call to emergency services, a pick-up truck that didn't see the hole or their car drove straight over them, but amazingly didn't add to their injuries.

While on the phone to the 911 dispatcher, Pineda can be heard wailing, 'Oh my God, no! Another car!'.

In audio released of the phone call, the pick-up truck driver can be heard running over to the sinkhole to offer help to the stricken mother and son.

He can be heard shouting to them, 'Did I just driver on top of you? Oh my God!'

